query:
WITH to_publish AS (
            SELECT id
            FROM nats.out
            WHERE subject = $1
            ORDER BY id
            FOR UPDATE SKIP LOCKED
            LIMIT $2
        ),
        deleted AS (
            DELETE FROM nats.out
            USING to_publish
            WHERE nats.out.id = to_publish.id
            RETURNING nats.out.id, nats.out.subject, nats.out.headers, nats.out.data
        )
        SELECT id, subject, headers, data
        FROM deleted
        ORDER BY id;
